\int {x^{n-2} \over (1+x)^n} {\rm d} x = \int (1+x)^{-2} \left({x \over 1+x}\right)^{n-2} {\rm d} x =\int y^{n-2} {\rm d} y
y = {x \over 1 + x}
t=1+x
y=1/t
